                <p>The latest edition of Steam Next Fest is over, and Steam has shared its list of the 50 most-played demos from the week-long event. This year's list was pretty heavy with horror, adventure, RPG, and simulation games. And surprisingly, only a few roguelike and racing titles.</p><p>One of the most unusual titles was Final Sentence, a battle-royale typing game that has a fatal ending for any player who can't keep up with the pace.</p><p data-embed-type="video" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kZSfblvkuro" data-width="100%" data-height="100%">          <iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/kZSfblvkuro" height="100%" width="100%" scrolling="no" frameborder="" webkitallowfullscreen="" mozallowfullscreen="" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p>Another title that caught our eye was The Cube, Save Us: an extraction shooter with a very arresting visual style.</p><p data-embed-type="video" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mKEoM5N-Eyg" data-width="100%" data-height="100%">          <iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/mKEoM5N-Eyg" height="100%" width="100%" scrolling="no" frameborder="" webkitallowfullscreen="" mozallowfullscreen="" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p>We've had our eye on <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/marvel-cosmic-invasion/" data-ref-id="5000-670015">Marvel Cosmic Invasion</a> for a while, so it wasn't too shocking to see that on the list. However, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/star-trek-voyager-across-the-unknown/" data-ref-id="5000-691471">Star Trek: Voyager - Across the Unknown</a>, was unexpected and it offers an intriguing glimpse at a chance to rewrite some of the stories that took place on that series.</p><p data-embed-type="video" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bqYgGynR3iU" data-width="100%" data-height="100%">          <iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/bqYgGynR3iU" height="100%" width="100%" scrolling="no" frameborder="" webkitallowfullscreen="" mozallowfullscreen="" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p>Most of the games that made the list either have active demos that can still be downloaded, or they're already in early access. The next installment of Steam Next Fest is scheduled for February 2026, but the complete list of the 50 most-played demos from this month's event is reproduced below.</p><h2>50 Most-Played Steam Next Fest Demos From October 2025</h2><ol><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2397300/Half_Sword?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Half Sword (medieval swordplay sim)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3241970?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Heroes of Might and Magic: Olden Era (turn-based strategy)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3834090/YAPYAP?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">YAPYAP (horror comedy co-op)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4021860?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Final Sentence (horror typing battle royle simulation)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4019420?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">REANIMAL (adventure horror co-op)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4028270?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Everwind (co-op open-world RPG)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2795540/The_Midnight_Walkers?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Midnight Walkers (zombie horror extraction-shooter)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3810880/THE_CUBE_SAVE_US?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Cube, Save Us (extraction-shooter)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4059420?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Misery (survival-horror co-op)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3179350/Long_Drive_North_CoOp_RV_Simulator?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Long Drive North: Co-Op RV Simulator (survival-crafting open-world)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3772580?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Car Service Together (racing simulation)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3911640?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Roadside Research (co-op comedy simulation)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3583210/Crashout_Crew?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Crashout Crew (arcade driving)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3996940?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Servant of the Lake (puzzle-adventure)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4054540?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Star Trek: Voyager - Across the Unknown (roguelike space-sim)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4040960?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Tears of Metal (medieval action-roguelike)</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2300120/Painkiller?snr=1_614_615_nextfestmostplayed_100703" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel